ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of JULIE JAI of Toronto, Ontario, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum for Human Rights, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective February 5, 2019, in the place of Margaret S. Vandenberg, whose term will expired.
